# NeuroRead — Complete Architecture & Project Deep-Dive

## 1. What Is NeuroRead?

**NeuroRead** is an accessibility-first, AI-powered reading platform designed to reduce cognitive load for individuals with **dyslexia, ADHD**, and other reading difficulties. It combines **LLM-based text simplification**, **real-time NLP analytics**, **adaptive learning with research-backed ML models**, and a **deeply accessible frontend** into a single production-deployed full-stack application.

- **Live Frontend:** [https://nr-three-puce.vercel.app](https://nr-three-puce.vercel.app) (Vercel)
- **Live Backend API:** [https://neuroread-5icn.onrender.com](https://neuroread-5icn.onrender.com) (Render)

